      "ruleId": "ias1-r001",
      "paragraphReference": "IAS 1.10",
      "ruleText": "A complete set of financial statements comprises a statement of financial position, a statement of profit or loss and other comprehensive income, a statement of changes in equity, a statement of cash flows, and notes.",
